1.02.name: wordpress/hierarchical-checkboxes-for-contact-form-7
1.02.description: After looking around for a hierarchical selection field in Contact Form 7 with no luck, we have decided to create our own plugin to help out other developers with a similar problem. This plugin allows a hierarchical list of check boxes, controlled via the WordPress menus, to be placed into a Contact Form 7 form.
